item.title: JDK files
item.dc:creator: @508_Client 508_Client
item.description:
@508_Client wrote:

  1. Use a different compiler, I get the same issue with one. The compiler is probably looking for JDK 1.6.0_0 while you may have 1.6.0_5 etc.

  2. No you don’t need to compile, it only updates what you’ve added.

edit: I would help on IM but im on a computer that doesn’t have it.
